Inclusion Criteria:

* Patients must be 18 to 70 years old, signed ICF;
* At least 4 weeks after previous chemotherapy (6 weeks since nitrosoureas);
* KPS ≥ 60;
* Unilateral, Supratentorial, solitary lesion and not crossing the midline(exclude patients with little tumors near the resectable tumor ev
